cs.IR, cs.CL, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.DL 

The paper deals with personalized keyword extraction from web pages, which is a problem related to information retrieval (IR) and natural language processing (NLP). Hence, cs.IR and cs.CL are the most likely sub-categories. The paper also proposes a novel model for solving the problem, which involves machine learning techniques such as segmentation and classification, making it relevant to sub-categories such as cs.LG, cs.AI, and cs.DL.
